flowchart TD
  A[Start script] --> B[Create output folder and timestamped run summary file]
  B --> C{FORCE_FRESH_AUTH_EACH_RUN?}
  C -->|Yes| D[Delete local token cache file if present]
  C -->|No| E[Keep existing token cache file]
  D --> F[Load MSAL SerializableTokenCache]
  E --> F

  F --> G[Create MSAL PublicClientApplication for organizations authority]
  G --> H{Cached SSO account available?}
  H -->|Yes| I[Use cached SSO account]
  H -->|No| J[Run interactive sign-in on localhost port 8400]

  J --> K{Access token returned?}
  K -->|No| L[Write SSO error file and exit]
  K -->|Yes| M[Extract signed-in username from id_token_claims]

  I --> N[Set authenticated username]
  M --> N

  N --> O[For each tenant in TENANTS]
  O --> P[Build tenant authority and create tenant MSAL client]
  P --> Q[Find tenant account in shared token cache]
  Q --> R[Acquire token silently then force refresh fallback]

  R --> S{Access token available?}
  S -->|No| T[Write tenant auth_error file]
  T --> U{More tenants?}

  S -->|Yes| V[Decode JWT tid claim]
  V --> W{tid equals requested tenant?}
  W -->|No| X[Write tenant auth_error file for tid mismatch]
  X --> U

  W -->|Yes| Y[POST KQL query to Graph security runHuntingQuery]
  Y --> Z{HTTP status 200?}
  Z -->|Yes| AA[Write tenant results JSON file]
  Z -->|No| AB[Write tenant Graph error file]

  AA --> U
  AB --> U
  U -->|Yes| O
  U -->|No| AC[Log run complete]

